{
  "stem": "3341.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went with pleasure, because I wanted to defend my country, despite the fact that it was a fascist country, but we were still a free republic.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When the war was declared, that was the start of the German war against the whole East.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was called to the army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We got uniforms like any other new recruit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the second day, they called all the Jewish boys in the-- I came to the army in Bratislava, which was the capital town of the country.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when I entered the army barracks with maybe about 30 other Jewish boys-- there were not many-- we were suddenly exchanged, the uniforms.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The captain, or whoever was in charge, they gave us shabby, dirty uniforms.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They said, from now on you are just bloody Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you will be in the army, but as a working-- as a working unit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't even know what was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I was-- I was in the army for about three weeks in Bratislava, in our hometown, and then they shipped us to the mountains.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have got a big range of mountains on the border, from Poland and Slovakia, that are equal to Alps.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Tatra.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They are Tatra mountains.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that is almost the whole area between Slovakia and Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Had a natural barrier between the two countries, because these high mountains-- like Alps in Germany or in Austria-- you can't just cross it or what is in Spain, the Pyrenees, something of that sort.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were sent the first 200-- they collected other Jewish soldiers from other [INAUDIBLE] zones in the area of Bratislava, and about 200 of us were shipped by train to the border of Poland.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was about three weeks before the Polish war started.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
